cs.CL, cs.SD, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SI 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on improving Automatic Speech Recognition (ASR) systems for a minority language, Uyghur, using a morpheme-based decoder. 
- cs.SD (Sound) is also a likely category as the paper deals with speech recognition and noise reduction. 
- cs.LG (Learning) is a possible category as the paper mentions training deeper and wider neural network acoustic models. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper deals with developing a more efficient and effective ASR system. 
- cs.SI (Signal Processing) is a possible category as the paper deals with processing speech signals and reducing noise.
